text: Vicente de Araújo Neto (born 1 October 1966) is a Brazilian equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Brazil Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Belo Horizonte
